library(tidyverse)
library(ggplot2)

load(file='ExpImp.RData')

data <- filter(ExpImp, !str_detect(ExpImp$, '| |  '))

for (col_name in colnames(data)[colnames(data) != ""]) {
  data[[col_name]] <- as.numeric(gsub("-", NA, data[[col_name]]))
}

dataMet <- select(data, c("", "", ""))

, 

fullExport <- select_at(data, vars(matches("")))
fullImport <- select_at(data, vars(matches("")))

dataMet$ <- rowSums(fullExport, na.rm = TRUE)
dataMet$ <- rowSums(fullImport, na.rm = TRUE)

dataMet <- dataMet[complete.cases(dataMet),]
coupledData <- select(dataMet, -c("", ""))
dataMet <- select(dataMet, c("", "", ""))
print(dataMet)
